title: Known and Undiscovered Oil in the World (Except U.S.) - Assessment Unit (2000)
name: Known and Undiscovered Oil in the World (Except U.S.) - Assessment Unit (2000)
description:
This dataset provides information on known and undiscovered oil contained in fields within the USGS-defined Assessment Units. An assesment unit is a volume of rock that contains fields with similar characteristics.

Note:  -9999 are missing values
